io.spine.server.entity

Class CommandDispatchingPhase<I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.entity.Phase<I,java.util.List<io.spine.core.Event>>
      • io.spine.server.entity.CommandDispatchingPhase<I>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of entity ID

    @Internal
public class CommandDispatchingPhase<I>
extends Phase<I,java.util.List<io.spine.core.Event>>
    A phase that dispatched a command to the entity in transaction.

    The result of such dispatch is always a List of events as described in the CommandHandlingEntity contract.
